## File field

This field type can be used to upload (or select from media library) one or multiple files.

## General options

- Field name
- Field key
- Description
- Is Required
- CSS Classes

## Specific options

- **Allowed file types:** Choose the file types allowed e.g image formats, pdf, zip, mp4 and many others (preview below)
- **Maximum file count:** Select the number of images allowed
- **Max file size (kB):**Â Set the max file size per attachment
